<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es-AR">
<link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.6/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
  integrity="sha384-4Q6Gf2aSP4eDXB8Miphtr37CMZZQ5oXLH2yaXMJ2w8e2ZtHTl7GptT4jmndRuHDT" crossorigin="anonymous">
<%- include ('../partials/head') %>

  <body>
    <%- include ('../partials/header') %>
      <main>
        <h2>¡Formulario pre-adopción!</h2>
        <form action="/adoptions/preAdopt/<%= animal.id %>" method="POST" class="row">
          <div class="col-12 col-lg-4 mb-5">
            <h3>Estas adoptando a <%= animal.name %>
            </h3>
            <hr>
            <img width="100%" src="/images/<%= animal.image %> " alt="">
          </div>
          <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-4">
            <h3>Contanos sobre vos</h3>
            <hr>
            <div class="mb-3">
              <input style="width: 100%;" type="text" name="name" placeholder=" Tu nombre" id="name" value="<%= (locals.oldData && oldData.name) && oldData.name %>"/>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-3">
              <input style="width: 100%;" type="text" name="surname" placeholder=" Tu apellido" id="surname" value="<%= (locals.oldData && oldData.surname) && oldData.surname %>"/>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-3">
              <input style="width: 100%;" type="email" name="email" id="email" placeholder="Email de contacto" value="<%= (locals.oldData && oldData.email) && oldData.email %>"/>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-3">
              <input style="width: 100%;" type="number" id="phone" name="phone" placeholder="Ingresa tu teléfono" value="<%= (locals.oldData && oldData.phone) && oldData.phone %>"/>
            </div>
            <div class="mb">
              <textarea style="width: 100%;" id="reasons" name="reasons" rows="5"
                placeholder="Contanos por qué querés adoptar"><%= (locals.oldData && oldData.reasons) && oldData.reasons %></textarea>
            </div>
            <% if (locals.errors) { %>
              <div class="alert alert-danger">
                <ul style="text-align: start; padding: 0;">
                  <% for (let error of errors.errors) { %>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-times"></i> <%= error.msg %></li>
                  <% } %>
                </ul>
              </div>
            <% } %>
           
          </div>
          <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-4">
            <h3>Contanos sobre tu vivienda</h3>
            <hr>
            <div class="mb-4">
              <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; justify-content: space-between;">
                <div>
                  <label for="dwelling">¿Qué tipo de vivienda tenés?</label>
                  <div style="display: flex; gap: 10px; justify-content: center;">
                    <input name="rent" class="form-check-input" style="width: 18px;" type="checkbox" value="1"
                      id="checkDefault">
                    <label class="form-check-label" for="checkDefault">
                      Alquilo
                    </label>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <select id="dwelling" name="dwelling" style="width: 60%;">
                  <option value="Casa">Casa</option>
                  <option value="Departamento">Departamento</option>
                  <option value="PH">PH</option>
                  <option value="Quinta">Quinta</option>
                </select>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-4">
              <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 20px; justify-content: space-between;">
                <label style="text-align: start;">¿Se permiten mascotas donde vives?</label>
                <div style="display: flex; gap: 20px; align-items: center;">
                  <div style="display: flex; gap: 10px; justify-content: center;">
                    <input name="petsAllowed" class="form-check-input" style="width: 18px;" type="radio" value="1"
                      id="checkDefault">
                    <label class="form-check-label" for="checkDefault">
                      Sì
                    </label>
                  </div>
                  <div style="display: flex; gap: 10px; justify-content: center;">
                    <input name="petsAllowed" class="form-check-input" style="width: 18px;" type="radio" value="0"
                      id="checkDefault">
                    <label class="form-check-label" for="checkDefault">
                      No
                    </label>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>


            </div>
            <div class="mb-4">
              <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 20px; justify-content: space-between;">
                <label style="text-align: start;">¿Alguien en tu hogar tiene alergia a perros o gatos?</label>
                <div style="display: flex; gap: 20px; align-items: center;">
                  <div style="display: flex; gap: 10px; justify-content: center;">
                    <input name="allergy" class="form-check-input" style="width: 18px;" type="radio" value="1"
                      id="checkDefault">
                    <label class="form-check-label" for="checkDefault">
                      Sì
                    </label>
                  </div>
                  <div style="display: flex; gap: 10px; justify-content: center;">
                    <input name="allergy" class="form-check-input" style="width: 18px;" type="radio" value="0"
                      id="checkDefault">
                    <label class="form-check-label" for="checkDefault">
                      No
                    </label>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-4">
              <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 20px;justify-content: space-between;">
                <label style="text-align: start;">En caso afirmativo ¿recibe tratamiento?</label>
                <div style="display: flex; gap: 20px; align-items: center;">
                  <div style="display: flex; gap: 10px; justify-content: center;">
                    <input name="underTreatment" class="form-check-input" style="width: 18px;" type="radio" value="1"
                      id="checkDefault">
                    <label class="form-check-label" for="checkDefault">
                      Sì
                    </label>
                  </div>
                  <div style="display: flex; gap: 10px; justify-content: center;">
                    <input name="underTreatment" class="form-check-input" style="width: 18px;" type="radio" value="0"
                      id="checkDefault">
                    <label class="form-check-label" for="checkDefault">
                      No
                    </label>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="clas my-5">
              <p
                style="text-align: start; border: 1px gray solid; padding: 10px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);">
                Hasta acá llegó el formulario de adopción. Habiendo leído los
                requisitos y completado el formulario,¿Sentís que estás dispuesto a
                adoptar responsablemente darle el hogar y la vida que merece?
                Nosotras buscamos adopciones responsables y para toda la vida. Una mascota no
                se descarta,no se regala,no se maltrata y no se abandona.
              </p>
              <div class="d-flex gap-2 justify-content-center mt-5">
                <button class="btn btn-secondary" type="button" onclick="window.history.back();">No estoy seguro
                  todavía</button>
                <button class="btn btn-dark" type="submit">Sí. Quiero adoptar</button>
              </div>

            </div>
          </div>








        </form>
      </main>
